    {
      "id": "n_problem",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "# Return Trip / Triangle Engine Canvas\n\nGoal: convert weak direct returns into profitable earning loops.\n\nCore question: after A -> B delivery, should the truck return directly, wait, move to C, or enter a triangle/quad loop?",
