      "id": "n_lane_examples",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## Directional Lane Truth\n\nDo not store only A <-> B.\n\nStore:\n- A -> B\n- B -> A\n\nBecause volume, rate, delay and return probability are asymmetric.",
