    {
      "id": "n_decision",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "# Decision Layer\n\nFor every completed A -> B trip, choose one:\n\n1. Direct B -> A return\n2. B -> C -> A triangle\n3. B -> C -> D -> A quad\n4. Wait for better load\n5. Reposition empty only if strategic\n6. Escalate to dispatcher/control tower\n\nPrimary optimization target:\nRevenue per vehicle day, not just shortest distance.",
      "x": 1040,
      "y": -700,
      "width": 520,
      "height": 310
    },
    {
      "id": "n_scoring_formula",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## Triangle Approval Formula\n\nApprove if:\n\ntriangle_score >= 70\nAND route_chain_reliability passes\nAND payment reliability passes\nAND vehicle/cargo/hub compatibility passes\nAND expected wait time is acceptable\nAND revenue per vehicle day improves.\n\nReject if any compliance or safety gate fails.",
      "x": 1040,
      "y": -280,
      "width": 520,
      "height": 260
    },
    {
      "id": "n_agent_rules",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## Agent Decisions\n\nMatching Agent:\n- finds B -> C and C -> A candidates\n\nPricing Agent:\n- applies return-leg incentive or risk premium\n\nRisk Agent:\n- blocks low-confidence, low-reliability, unsafe cargo combinations\n\nControl Tower:\n- handles exception, premium cargo, or low-confidence route chains",
      "x": 1040,
      "y": 100,
      "width": 520,
      "height": 260
    },
    {
      "id": "n_data_model",
      "type": "file",
      "file": "10_Data_Model/Docs/Zippy Logistics Analytics Star Schema.md",
      "x": 1040,
      "y": 470,
      "width": 520,
      "height": 240
    },
    {
      "id": "n_calendar",
      "type": "file",
      "file": "10_Data_Model/Docs/dim_time India Logistics Calendar.md",
      "x": 1040,
      "y": 800,
      "width": 520,
      "height": 220
    },
    {
      "id": "n_mvp",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "# MVP Validation Routes\n\n1. Tiruppur -> Chennai -> Coimbatore -> Tiruppur\n2. Erode -> Chennai -> Coimbatore -> Erode\n3. Bengaluru -> Sri City -> Chennai -> Bengaluru\n\nMeasure for 14 days:\n- direct return load availability\n- B -> C load availability\n- C -> A load availability\n- wait time\n- empty km\n- revenue per vehicle day\n- driver acceptance\n- payment reliability\n- delay/reliability score",
      "x": 1720,
      "y": -700,
      "width": 520,
      "height": 350
    },
